        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer200414219" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4381382885366562660">hey, this is my book, so of course I love it. When it comes to my own writing, I like to give it the test is time. If I still love the book when I re-read it months after having finished it, then I did a good job. And when I re-read Scorpio Rising, I once again got completely swept away in the lives and passions of the characters. <br/>Please read it, and let me know what you think,<br/>Monique</span>

          </span>
